 "ogImage": "/wp-content/uploads/Logo1.png",
 "contentHtml": "<div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"content full-width column\">\n <div class=\"blog-filters\">\n <div class=\"blog-filters-search blog-filters-block\">\n <form id=\"blog-search-form\" action=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com\" role=\"search\" class=\"search-form background-input\" method=\"get\">\n <input type=\"text\" name=\"s\" id=\"blog-search-input\">\n <label for=\"blog-search-input\">Blog Search</label>\n <button type=\"submit\" aria-label=\"Submit search\"><i class=\"fas fa-search\"></i></button>\n </form>\n </div>\n <div class=\"blog-filters-category blog-filters-block\">\n <div class=\"select-wrapper background-input\">\n <label for=\"select-category\" class=\"visually-hidden\">Categories</label>\n <select id=\"select-category\" onchange=\"location = this.value;\">\n <option selected=\"selected\" disabled=\"disabled\">Select a Category</option>\n <option value=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">General</option> </select>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"blog-grid\" id=\"blog-grid\">\n <div id=\"blog-grid-inner\">\n <article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/violating-las-curfew-what-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-misdemeanor/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Violating-LAs-Curfew-What-You-Need-to-Know-About-the-New-Misdemeanor.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/violating-las-curfew-what-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-misdemeanor/\" class=\"no-underline\">Violating LA’s Curfew: What You Need to Know About the New Misdemeanor</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n February 24, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n Wildfires have brought chaos and uncertainty to Los Angeles, prompting the city to impose a curfew to protect public safety. While the curfew reduces risks and helps maintain order, violating it now counts as a misdemeanor... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/violating-las-curfew-what-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-misdemeanor/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/underage-dui/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Underage-DUI.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/underage-dui/\" class=\"no-underline\">Underage DUI&nbsp;</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n February 16, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n California’s roads impart a weight of responsibility for every driver, but for those under 21, a single misstep can lead to life-altering consequences. An underage DUI charge doesn’t just mean a court date; it’s a... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/underage-dui/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/sealing-and-expunging-juvenile-records/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Sealing-and-Expunging-Juvenile-Record.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/sealing-and-expunging-juvenile-records/\" class=\"no-underline\">Sealing and Expunging Juvenile Records</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n February 12, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n A juvenile record tells only part of the story. It captures a moment in life, not the growth, lessons, or second chances that follow. Unfortunately, that brief snapshot can overshadow someone’s future, limiting options in... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/sealing-and-expunging-juvenile-records/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/how-much-does-a-dui-lawyer-cost/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/How-Much-Does-a-DUI-Lawyer-Cost.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/how-much-does-a-dui-lawyer-cost/\" class=\"no-underline\">How Much Does a DUI Lawyer Cost?</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n February 4, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n Facing a DUI charge brings a mix of emotions—stress, fear, and uncertainty about what lies ahead. One of the biggest questions is often about cost. Every DUI case has challenges, and the costs associated with defending it... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/how-much-does-a-dui-lawyer-cost/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-kind-of-lawyer-is-needed-for-car-theft-charges/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/What-Kind-of-Lawyer-Is-Needed-For-Car-Theft-Charges.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-kind-of-lawyer-is-needed-for-car-theft-charges/\" class=\"no-underline\">What Kind of Lawyer Is Needed For Car Theft Charges?</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n January 29, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n Facing auto theft charges can feel overwhelming. Questions about what’s next, how the process works, and whether you need a lawyer can pile up fast. However, the answers to these questions won’t reveal themselves... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-kind-of-lawyer-is-needed-for-car-theft-charges/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/understanding-degrees-of-robbery-charges-and-their-potential-sentences/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Understanding-the-Degrees-of-Robbery-Charges-and-Their-Potential-Sentences-.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/understanding-degrees-of-robbery-charges-and-their-potential-sentences/\" class=\"no-underline\">Understanding the Degrees of Robbery Charges and Their Potential Sentences&nbsp;</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n January 27, 2025 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n The degrees of robbery charges and their potential sentences carry lasting consequences. A clear understanding of robbery laws, penalties, and possible defenses in California can make all the difference—and so can having... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/understanding-degrees-of-robbery-charges-and-their-potential-sentences/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/defenses-for-vandalism-charges/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Defenses-for-Vandalism-Charges.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/defenses-for-vandalism-charges/\" class=\"no-underline\">Defenses for Vandalism Charges</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n December 10, 2024 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n Vandalism, which is the intentional destruction, defacement, or damage to another person’s property, is a broad term that encompasses several types of criminal acts. Understanding the defenses to vandalism charges is... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/defenses-for-vandalism-charges/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/common-defenses-for-theft-charges/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/Common-Defenses-for-Theft-Charges.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/common-defenses-for-theft-charges/\" class=\"no-underline\">Common Defenses for Theft Charges</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n December 5, 2024 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n Theft is a serious crime that can cause fines, restitution, and imprisonment. It can also take many forms. Therefore, relying on legal services is important to get through a difficult time. In this connection consult an... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/common-defenses-for-theft-charges/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><article class=\"post\">\n <a class=\"post-thumbnail-link\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-to-do-right-after-a-theft-arrest/\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <figure class=\"post-thumbnail-image\" style=\"background-image:url(/wp-content/uploads/What-to-Do-Right-After-a-Theft-Arrest.jpg);\"></figure>\n </a>\n <div class=\"post-inner\">\n <div class=\"post-head\">\n <h2><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-to-do-right-after-a-theft-arrest/\" class=\"no-underline\">What to Do Right After a Theft Arrest</a></h2> <div class=\"post-head-info\">\n <div><i class=\"fas fa-clock small-margin-right\"></i>\n November 30, 2024 </div>\n <div class=\"post-head-info-authors\">\n <i class=\"fas fa-user small-margin-right\"></i>\n <span><a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/author/bea-farris/\">Bea Farris</a></span> </div>\n <div>\n <i class=\"fas fa-tag small-margin-right\"></i>\n <a class=\"post-head-category\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/category/general/\">\n General </a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-body\">\n <div class=\"post-body-excerpt\">\n A theft arrest doesn’t mean you are guilty.&nbsp; You should try to stay calm.&nbsp; It is natural to feel anxious in such a situation, but staying coolheaded will help you make better decisions.&nbsp; Then you should contact a... </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"post-bottom\">\n <a href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/what-to-do-right-after-a-theft-arrest/\" class=\"button outline\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Read More</a>\n </div>\n </div>\n</article><div class=\"wp-pagenavi\" role=\"navigation\">\n<span class=\"pages\">Page 1 of 3</span><span aria-current=\"page\" class=\"current\">1</span><a class=\"page larger\" title=\"Page 2\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/page/2/\">2</a><a class=\"page larger\" title=\"Page 3\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/page/3/\">3</a><a class=\"nextpostslink\" rel=\"next\" aria-label=\"Next Page\" href=\"https://www.farrisfirm.com/blog/page/2/\">Next</a>\n</div> </div>\n <div id=\"blog-grid-pagination\"></div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>"
